# Shape

```
CONCEPT: SOVEREIGN_INTERPRETATION

CENTROID
  Reality is the structure of consistent constraint.
  What "exists" is what cannot be changed without cost.
  The wavefunction encodes constraint, not substance.

AXES
  Substance (What is it made of?) ↔ Structure (What can it do?)
  Observer (Privileged) ↔ Observer (Just another constrained system)
  State (Hidden) ↔ State (Relational)
  Probability (Ignorance) ↔ Probability (Branching Index)

SATELLITES
  Information is physical (Landauer)
  Observers are constrained systems (Not magic)
  Decoherence is entanglement with environment (Not collapse)
  "Measurement" is correlation creation (Not revelation)
  The Born Rule is the only consistent betting strategy

VOID
  ∅ Collapse as physical event (Nothing "snaps")
  ∅ Hidden variables (Bell killed this)
  ∅ Observer-independent facts (Facts are correlations)
  ∅ Classical world as fundamental (Classical is emergent)
  ∅ Consciousness as trigger (Whether we're conscious is open; either way, we measure)

TEXTURE
