# The Hypothesis (Testable?)

間

        If structure > substance,
        then information is the primitive.

        Prediction:
                Any system that processes information
                        is a valid "observer."
                
                Including: thermostats, rocks, AIs.
                
                "Observation" is just correlation creation.
                It happens constantly.
                It is not special.

        Implication:
                The classical world is not "where collapse happens."
                The classical world is "where decoherence is fast."
                
                We live in the quantum world.
                We just can't see the coherence anymore.

